The evidence with the title 'Summary of latest federal income tax data - tax foundation ' says Dec 22, 2014  ... Top 50 percent of all taxpayers paid 97.2 percent of all federal income taxes ; top 1 percent paid 38.1 percent ; and bottom 90 percent paid 29.7 percent of all federal income  ... The top 1 percent 's average effective tax rate for 2012 of 22.8 percent was slightly lower than that of 2011 ( 23.5 percent). 
